class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Domain\\Message\\StartRun"
type: readonly final class
summary: A domain event representing the initiation of a specific execution run within the agent core. It encapsulates the unique identifiers and sequence metadata required to track the lifecycle of a single run instance. This class serves as a value object for conveying run start context across domain boundaries.
